; Coverage test for xact.cc lines 640-641, 644-654
; Tests the rounding adjustment path in transaction finalization.
; When per-unit costs produce rounding artifacts, the finalize code
; checks if the imbalance is explained by rounding differences.
; Total cost (@@) postings should be skipped in this check.
; This requires a transaction with per-unit cost that causes rounding.

2024/01/01 Buy at per-unit price with rounding
    Assets:Brokerage         3 AAPL @ $33.33
    Assets:Brokerage         2 AAPL @@ $66.67
    Assets:Cash            $-166.66

test bal
            $-166.66
              5 AAPL  Assets
              5 AAPL    Brokerage
            $-166.66    Cash
--------------------
            $-166.66
              5 AAPL
end test
